      public boolean equals (TVShow S)
      checks if the TV Show is equal to the given TV Show.
      Parameters:
      S - the TV Show to be compared.
      Returns:
      true if the TV Shows are equal, false otherwise. two TV Shows are equal if they have the same showName, startTime and endTime.

    • isOnSameTime

      public String isOnSameTime (TVShow S)
      Checks if the TV Show is on the same time as the given TV Show.
      Specified by:
      isOnSameTime in interface Watchable
      Parameters:
      S - the TV Show to be compared.
      Returns:
      "Same time" if the TV Shows are on the same time, "Some Overlap" if they overlap, and "Different time" otherwise. 1. "Same time" if both startTime and endTime of S and this show are the same 2. "Some Overlap" if either the startTime or endTime of the TV Show is between the startTime and endTime of the compared TV Show S 3. "Different time" if neither of the above conditions are true
